<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>auto_scanner report - $target</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0d1117;
    --panel: #161b22;
    --panel-2: #1c2230;
    --border: #30363d;
    --text: #e6edf3;
    --muted: #8b949e;
    --accent: #58a6ff;
    --critical: #ff5c5c;
    --high: #ff8b3d;
    --medium: #f1c40f;
    --low: #3fb950;
    --info: #58a6ff;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Inter",
                 Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  header {
    padding: 28px 32px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #161b22 0%, #0d1117 100%);
  }
  header h1 {
    margin: 0 0 6px 0;
    font-size: 22px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }
  header .meta {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 13px;
    word-break: break-all;
  }
  .warning {
    margin: 16px 32px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    background: #3a1d1d;
    border: 1px solid #6b2a2a;
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: #ffb4b4;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  main { padding: 8px 32px 64px; }
  section { margin-top: 28px; }
  h2 {
    font-size: 16px;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.2px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .card {
    background: var(--panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
  }
  .card .num {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .card .label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    background: var(--panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  th, td {
    padding: 10px 14px;
    text-align: left;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    vertical-align: top;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  th {
    background: var(--panel-2);
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .pill {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 2px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .pill.critical { background: rgba(255,92,92,0.18);  color: var(--critical); border: 1px solid rgba(255,92,92,0.4); }
  .pill.high     { background: rgba(255,139,61,0.18); color: var(--high);     border: 1px solid rgba(255,139,61,0.4); }
  .pill.medium   { background: rgba(241,196,15,0.18); color: var(--medium);   border: 1px solid rgba(241,196,15,0.4); }
  .pill.low      { background: rgba(63,185,80,0.18);  color: var(--low);      border: 1px solid rgba(63,185,80,0.4); }
  .pill.info     { background: rgba(88,166,255,0.18); color: var(--info);     border: 1px solid rgba(88,166,255,0.4); }
  .endpoint { font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace; word-break: break-all; }
  .desc { color: var(--text); white-space: pre-wrap; }
  .finding-details {
    margin-top: 10px;
    padding-top: 10px;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--border);
    color: var(--muted);
    white-space: normal;
  }
  .finding-details code {
    color: var(--text);
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    word-break: break-word;
  }
  .finding-details ol { margin: 6px 0 0 18px; padding: 0; }
  .severity-block { margin-top: 24px; }
  .severity-block h3 { margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; }
  footer {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 12px;
    padding: 24px 32px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .tool-link { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
  .tool-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .empty {
    background: var(--panel);
    border: 1px dashed var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 28px;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .muted { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <h1>auto_scanner vulnerability report</h1>
  <div class="meta">
    <strong>Target:</strong> $target<br />
    <strong>Run ID:</strong> $run_id &nbsp;|&nbsp;
    <strong>Generated:</strong> $generated_at &nbsp;|&nbsp;
    <strong>Findings:</strong> $total_findings
  </div>
</header>

<div class="warning">
  EDUCATIONAL USE ONLY. Only test systems you own or have explicit
  written authorisation to assess. The maintainers accept no liability
  for misuse of this tool.
</div>

<main>
  <section>
    <h2>Executive summary</h2>
    $executive_summary
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Discovery summary</h2>
    $discovery_summary
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Severity summary</h2>
    <div class="cards">
      $severity_cards
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Tool summary</h2>
    $tool_table
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Report sections</h2>
    $section_table
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>OWASP summary</h2>
    $owasp_table
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>OWASP coverage matrix</h2>
    <p class="muted">
      For each tracked OWASP family, the matrix shows whether this run produced
      at least one validated vulnerability or exploit achievement mapped to that
      category. Passive observations stay in the report, but do not count as
      coverage.
    </p>
    $coverage_matrix
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Findings</h2>
    $findings_html
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  Generated by auto_scanner $version. Raw tool output is preserved next
  to this report under the <code>raw/</code> directory.
</footer>
</body>
</html>
